Package com.ibm.team.repository.common Description

Provides APIs for the Repository component that are common to both the client-side and the server-side.

Package Specification

Provides APIs for the Repository component that are common to both the client-side and the server-side. This includes the exception hierarchy (rooted at TeamRepositoryException), the main service interface (IRepositoryService), and the item and item handle hierarchies (rooted at IItem and IItemHandle, respectively).
